        <p>Welcome to Fern & Flourish Co., a place where nature's beauty meets intentional planning. Our journey began with a simple idea: that the tools we use to organize our lives should be as beautiful and grounding as a walk in the woods.</p>
        
        <p>Founded on a passion for botanical illustration and the art of slow living, we create planners that aren't just about productivity, but about presence. Each page is designed to offer a moment of calm in a busy world, with wildflowers, forest motifs, and elegant typography that inspires you to flourish.</p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To provide creative professionals and intentional-living enthusiasts with planning systems that nourish the spirit and simplify the day. We believe in the power of daily encouragement and the timeless wisdom of nature.</p>
